steps.name: I am on the Associated Trials screen
I have selected the Add button
I am on the Add Associated Trial screen
I must enter the Trial Identifier
I click the Look Up Trial button
the Requested Trial is retrieved from the respective system (CTRP for NCI and ClinicalTrials.gov for NCT)
I have clicked the Save button
the associated study displays on the Associated Trials screen
the Associated Trial will be associated with the trial
I can select the <trialIdentifier> and the trial is <Retrievedfrom> displayed
